sources.title: A Big Heist in Los Angeles 1963 - Would You Trust the Devil’s Right Hand? Aram Katcher film
sources.description:
After robbing an amphitheater and eliminating his accomplices, a ruthless gangster discovers the only witness to his crime is the unassuming female cashier he overlooked.

Original title: The Right Hand of the Devil (1963)
Directed by Aram Katcher

Main cast:
Aram Katcher - Pepe Lusara
Lisa McDonald - Miss Sutherland
Brad Trumbull - Williams
James V. Christy - Sammy
Chris Randall - Spooky
Monte Lee - Carter
Luigi Gardneri - Dino's Bartender
Georgia Holden - The Dancer
Jack Elton - Dino's Pianist

Genres: Crime Drama, Audio commentary
Release date: July 1, 1963 
Filming location: Los Angeles, California, USA


Black & White version: https://youtu.be/lbmBaMExZLg
